My Life on a Plate

Chef Brian Turner takes celebrities back to their youths, using the power of food to jog colourful memories.

_____________________________________________

My Life on a Plate
Episode 1 of 15
Mary Berry

Mary Berry journeys back to her childhood haunts in Bath and reveals that she was an outdoorsy child and naughty at school! She and Brian Turner visit key locations that resonate with Mary, prompting heartwarming memories of a happy childhood.

Brian is inspired to cook two dishes - one full of nostalgia to remind Mary of her mum's home baking, the other a tribute to Mary, drawing on different aspects of her younger years
